---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — KAIRA"
  description="KAIRA's privacy policy: what information we collect through our website and quote form, and how we use and protect it."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-16 md:py-20">
    <p class="hud-label mb-3">LEGAL <span class="text-white/25">//</span> PRIVACY</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink md:text-4xl">Privacy <span class="grad-text">Policy</span></h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">Last updated: July 17, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose-kaira mt-8 space-y-8 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed [&_h2]:text-xl [&_h2]:font-bold [&_h2]:text-ink">
      <section>
        <h2>Information we collect</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          When you submit our quote request form, we collect the information you provide: your name,
          business name, email address, phone number, current website URL, requested services,
          estimated budget, and project details. We also use Cloudflare Turnstile to protect the
          form from spam, which may process technical information about your browser.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How we use it</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          We use the information you submit solely to respond to your inquiry, prepare a quote, and
          communicate with you about your project. We do not sell, rent, or share your information
          with third parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Service providers</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Our website is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Quote submissions are delivered to us by email
          via Resend. Payments, when applicable, are processed by Stripe. Each provider processes
          data under its own privacy policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Data retention</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          We keep inquiry emails for as long as needed to serve you and meet legal obligations. You
          may request deletion of your information at any time by contacting us.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Cookies & analytics</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          This site does not use advertising cookies. If we use privacy-respecting analytics, they
          collect aggregate usage data only.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Questions about this policy? Reach out through our <a href="/contact" class="font-medium text-purple hover:underline">contact form</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
